          },
          "manual": {
            "reason": "open-design needs its own `od` CLI, which is not auto-installable headlessly and collides with the unix `od` (octal-dump).",
            "steps": [
              "Install open-design (desktop app from open-design.ai, Docker, or build from source)",
              "Ensure open-designs `od` is first on PATH (the system /usr/bin/od shadows it)",
